new['JOB YEARS'] = 0
for i in range(len(new['Years in current job'])):
    #      - '10+ years'
    if new['Years in current job'].iloc[i] == '< 1 year':
        new['JOB YEARS'].iloc[i] = 0
    elif new['Years in current job'].iloc[i] == '1 year':
        new['JOB YEARS'].iloc[i] = 1
    elif new['Years in current job'].iloc[i] == '2 years':
        new['JOB YEARS'].iloc[i] = 2
    elif new['Years in current job'].iloc[i] == '3 years':
        new['JOB YEARS'].iloc[i] = 3
    elif new['Years in current job'].iloc[i] == '4 years':
        new['JOB YEARS'].iloc[i] = 4
    elif new['Years in current job'].iloc[i] == '5 years':
